na walang demonyong buto.

00:18:04.900 --> 00:18:06.019
Nagkaroon ka ng maling tao.

00:18:06.619 --> 00:18:07.859
Hindi ako babalik kasama ka.

00:18:08.859 --> 00:18:09.980
Sa ilalim ng Demon Heart Hall

00:18:10.299 --> 00:18:11.740
namamalagi ang sagradong bukal ng aming angkan

00:18:11.980 --> 00:18:12.819
tinatawag na Asura Spring.

00:18:13.299 --> 00:18:14.339
Mayroon itong mga katangian ng pagpapagaling.

00:18:15.299 --> 00:18:17.900
Miss Bai, kahit na tumanggi kang
maging Night Deity,

00:18:18.460 --> 00:18:19.900
mapapahusay mo pa ang iyong kapangyarihan

00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:21.019
at gumaling doon.

00:18:25.460 --> 00:18:26.259
Kung ganoon,

00:18:26.980 --> 00:18:27.619
tara na.

00:18:29.259 --> 00:18:30.259
Ito ang lugar ng Night Clan.

00:18:30.500 --> 00:18:31.500
Ito ay mapanganib.

00:18:31.980 --> 00:18:33.420
Habang may pag-asa,

00:18:34.019 --> 00:18:35.099
hindi tayo dapat sumuko.

00:18:35.859 --> 00:18:37.180
At sa antas ng aking paglilinang,

00:18:38.500 --> 00:18:39.380
Wala akong dapat ikatakot.

00:18:48.059 --> 00:18:49.380
Tapos hinihiling ko na samahan niya ako.

00:18:49.819 --> 00:18:51.019
At dapat mong garantiya

00:18:51.859 --> 00:18:53.099
hindi tayo maghihiwalay.

00:18:54.339 --> 00:18:55.180
Syempre.

00:19:13.900 --> 00:19:15.059
Hail the Night Deity!

00:19:16.259 --> 00:19:18.208
- Hail the Night Deity!
